ass="cartImg" src="http://yanxuan-static.nosdn.127.net/hxm/yanxuan-wap/p/20161201/style/img/icon-normal/noCart-d6193bd6e4.png?imageView&type=webp" mode></image><view class="hint">购物车还是空的，赶紧去购物吧</view></view></block></view>